fact or any proof," said Lieutenant General Stanislav Kavun,deputy
commander of the Russian Interior Troops.
</P>
<P>
He said Hawkes' statement was based solely on verbal accounts
from unnamed witnesses, and therefore should be seen "as a
provocation whose goal is to discredit the federal forces'
operation against the terrorists in Chechnya." 
