dissident has been ordered to leave after his two-week visa
expired.
</P>
<P>
Yandarbayev's stay in Pakistan caused a diplomatic row between
Russia and Pakistan.
</P>
<P>
Moscow blamed Islamabad for organizing the trip. However,
Pakistan rejected the claim,saying Yandarbayev was on a private
tour and has met no Pakistan officials during his stay. 
