<HEADLINE> HK Hosts Education, Career Exposition </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong is moving towards
a knowledge-based economy that calls for a high caliber workforce,
according to Michael C C Sze, executive director of the Hong Kong
Trade Development Council (TDC).
</P>
<P>
Speaking at the opening of the Education &AMP; Career Expo 2000
Thursday, Sze said both students and the working public of Hong
Kong have to equip themselves to tap new opportunities and meet
new challenge.
</P>
<P>
