totaling 275. In the education section, 219 institutions from Hong
Kong and abroad offer a wide selection of learning opportunities,
which include undergraduate and postgraduate programs, distance
learning courses, language and adult education courses, vocational
training, as well as the increasingly popular cyber education
opportunities. 
