<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Open Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, February 24 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks went up 135.
78 points, or 0.83 percent, to open at 16,512.57 Thursday.
</P>
